CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,FFifteen thousand people across Kent
OL,8,Fare still having water supply issues,
OL,9,Fas South East Water apologised to
OL,10,Fcustomers impacted.
OL,12,F8000 people in the Whitstable area
OL,13,Fhave no water at all, while 7000
OL,14,Fpeople are having either low pressure
OL,15,For intermittent supply in Tankerton,
OL,16,FAshford, Ulcombe, Cranbrook, Coxheath
OL,17,Fand Headcorn.
OL,19,FSouth East Water is asking people to
OL,20,Fonly use water for essential purposes
OL,21,Fsuch as drinking, washing and cooking.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
