OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,FThe company apologised for the
OL,8,Fdisruption to customers and says it is
OL,9,Fdoing everything it can to prevent and
OL,10,Fresolve the issues.
OL,12,FIn a statement South East Water's
OL,13,FIncident Manager, Steve Benton, said:
OL,14,F"Customers across Kent are still
OL,15,Fexperiencing water supply issues due
OL,16,Fto extremely high demand during the
OL,17,Fvery hot weather.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,F"Yesterday (Wednesday 27 May) we
OL,8,Fpumped 628 million litres of water to
OL,9,Fcustomers across our region. This is
OL,10,Fhigher than the average for this time
OL,11,Fof year, and over the weekend we were
OL,12,Ftreating and pumping more than 100
OL,13,Fmillion litres more than the daily
OL,14,Faverage for May.
OL,16,F"We are doing everything we can to get
OL,17,Ftreated water into our storage
OL,18,Freservoirs, but some customers will
OL,19,Fcontinue to have intermittent water
OL,20,Fsupply until these levels have been
OL,21,Frestored.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,F"Currently there are 8,000 customers
OL,8,Fwithout supply in the Whitstable area
OL,9,Fbecause the storage reservoirs which
OL,10,Fserve the area have reached a critical
OL,11,Flevel. We expect customers will start
OL,12,Fto see tap water supplies return later
OL,13,Ftoday, but this may be intermittent
OL,14,Fover the weekend.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,F"There are currently 7,000 customers
OL,8,Fexperiencing low pressure or an
OL,9,Fintermittent supply in Tankerton,
OL,10,FAshford and its surrounding areas,
OL,11,FUlcombe, Cranbrook, Coxheath and
OL,12,FHeadcorn. A further 7,000 customers
OL,13,Fare at risk of experiencing some
OL,14,Fsupply loss today.
OL,16,FMr Benton continued: "We are
OL,17,Fcontinuing to ask customers in supply
OL,18,Fto use water for essential purposes
OL,19,Fonly - for example drinking, washing
OL,20,Fand cooking.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,F"We have bottled water collection
OL,8,Fstations already set up and are
OL,9,Fmonitoring. Details of locations can
OL,10,Fbe found on our website.
OL,12,F"Our customer care team will continue
OL,13,Fto support our most vulnerable
OL,14,Fcustomers with deliveries of bottled
OL,15,Fwater.
OL,17,F"We are sorry to customers who have
OL,18,Fhad interruptions or low pressure in
OL,19,Ftheir water supply and know how
OL,20,Ffrustrating it is, especially in very
OL,21,Fhot weather.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,F"We will continue to do all we can to
OL,8,Fprevent and resolve the issues."
OL,10,FOn Thursday, Kent County Council said
OL,11,Fit will set up a new "strategic
OL,12,Fpartnership" to oversee water
OL,13,Fresilience in the county following the
OL,14,Flatest outages.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@VOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,FThe Kent Water Resilience Partnership
OL,8,Fwill be chaired by council leader
OL,9,FLinden Kemkaran and include water
OL,10,Fcompanies, local authorities,
OL,11,Fregulators and others to focus on
OL,12,Fplanning, performance and show
OL,13,Fpublicly how water issues are being
OL,14,Faddressed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,FMs Kemkaran said: "People across Kent
OL,8,Fare fed up with being left without
OL,9,Fwater or having their supply
OL,10,Fdisrupted, sometimes for days at a
OL,11,Ftime, and not getting clear answers
OL,12,Fabout what's gone wrong or when it
OL,13,Fwill be fixed.
OL,15,F"That's simply not good enough."
OL,17,FThe council boss said while the
OL,18,Fauthority does not have direct power
OL,19,Fover water companies, "we do have a
OL,20,Fresponsibility to stand up for Kent".
OL,26,@oD@SOUwD@AOUwD@`O]{D@WOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,FShe added: "At the moment,
OL,8,Fresponsibility is too fragmented and
OL,9,Fthere is no single place where the
OL,10,Fwhole system is being looked at.
OL,12,F"This partnership intends to change
OL,13,Fthat. It will shine a light on the
OL,14,Fissues affecting Kent and make sure
OL,15,Fthere is clear, open scrutiny of how
OL,16,Fthose responsible are responding."
OL,26,@oD@LOUtD@AOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
