OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,FThe move follows calls from the Green
OL,8,Fgroup at Kent County Council for the
OL,9,Fauthority to declare a "Kent Water
OL,10,FSupply Emergency" and create a plan to
OL,11,Frectify the situation if water supply
OL,12,Fin the county is not fit for purpose.
OL,14,FGreen councillor Stuart Heaver,
OL,15,Frepresenting a Whitstable ward, said
OL,16,Fon Wednesday: "It is unbelievable that
OL,17,Fonce again my residents are without
OL,18,Fwater. This madness just gets worse.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@QO]xD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
