PN,41312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780002672
OL,3,CFifteen thousand people having water
OL,4,Csupply issues as water company
OL,5,Capologises
OL,7,F"We need to find out if our water
OL,8,Fsupply is fit for purpose and resolve
OL,9,Fthis."
